        <num>CC 2606</num>
        <heading>2606.  Buyer's acceptance of nonconforming things</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2606.  Buyer's acceptance of nonconforming things
A buyer who, with knowledge, accepts nonconforming things may no longer reject those things on grounds of that nonconformity, unless the acceptance was made in the reasonable belief that the nonconformity would be cured.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=109664</p>
